.github/workflows/** @wesm
.github/scripts/** @wesm

# Security-critical configuration
.github/trusted-contributors.json @wesm
.github/CODEOWNERS @wesm

# Security documentation (good to review, not critical)
.github/SECURITY_BOT.md @wesm
SECURITY.md @wesm
